channel.title: onetake
channel.description: An original experimental music podcast from Lawrence, Kansas.
channel.itunes:subtitle: An original experimental music podcast from Lawrence, Kansas.
channel.itunes:author: Nate Haas
channel.itunes:summary: An incidental document of the sound, noise and music in my life. Each recording is ideally uninterrupted and unedited.

item.title: onetake 140
item.description: In his basement in Lawrence, Kansas, Nate recorded an Akai S612 (M-Audio O2, Fender Blues Junior) using an Edirol R4. The result was panned, equalized and compressed using old, stolen multitrack software on his desktop PC.
